{"tid":849242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禁止外國記者進入西藏    中國駐美大使：怕高原反應","createTime":"2018-10-05T14:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T04:49:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5830230e9cdb73bd892f0556432054db5bb573a1","tid":849242,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"據外媒報導，崔天凱日前應邀前往美國公廣電台受訪，被問到會不會允許外國學者、記者前往西藏等地區時，崔天凱表示因為西藏的海拔非常高，當地氣候可能也相當惡劣，因此暫時不建議外人前往；節目主持人追問「若這些惡劣條件都能被克服呢？」崔天凱因此說，「不是所有人都能快速的適應高原氣候」，還說中國要保護環境，因此對外來者人數管制，並稱「如果中國能妥善的『保護』這些東西，非常歡迎來自美國的參觀者」。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，崔天凱表示包括新疆在內，整個中國都對外國開放，「不過新疆最近有『恐怖主義』的問題，中國政府被迫採取相關措施」，並對外界質疑的「秘密拘留營」作出解釋，稱其實是「職業訓練營」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/禁止記者進入西藏-中國-怕高原反應-043517780.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%80%95%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89-043517780.html&d=LVeiHdKwMKcZ54QT6wQ44Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=28567981\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/禁止記者進入西藏-中國-怕高原反應-043517780.html</a>"},{"pid":"b9ea774e6db559dfa12543c83f1656d3cd9faa10","tid":849242,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb42c359f755732306a673159f2b93575ef82db","tid":849242,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d6257249766512283dcf676e3de3884329674e","tid":849242,"uid":187076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-0